name: The Crown of the 7 Chakras
description:
Here is my contribution for the #HEN500K event

The Crown - The Third Eye - The Throat - The Heart - The Solar Plexus - The Sacral - The Root  

Here is my perception of the 7 chakras for the moment, they are all mixed together, in the form of a crown, at the top of the skull, in an opposite alignment.
